{"word":"ἀνακλαίω","slug":"ἀνακλαίω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνακλαίω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Note also that there is another verb <a href='S:ἀνακλάω'><el>ἀνακλάω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to weep aloud, burst into tears</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to weep for</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; so in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}